Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give Tom-san back to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.85,0:00:36.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.19,0:00:39.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.69,0:00:43.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.03,0:00:51.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.00,0:01:01.70,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Working together, let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.72,0:01:09.08,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:15.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail-- let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.98,0:01:23.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.11,0:01:26.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey fraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.49,0:01:30.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most will be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.45,0:01:34.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.50,0:01:37.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.50,0:01:41.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.67,0:01:45.24,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.26,0:01:48.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.22,0:01:52.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.56,0:01:56.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up the pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.48,0:01:59.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.73,0:02:02.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.69,0:02:08.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag-- together, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.49,0:02:16.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your chief? Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please go ahead, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.18,0:02:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! It's hot! It's hot! It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.76,0:02:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I spilled the coffee!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.97,0:02:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Stupid coffee!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.68,0:02:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you there...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Cutty Flam?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.81,0:02:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hm?\N--It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.61,0:02:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought you'd survived that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to believe, but I'm happy to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.83,0:02:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:02:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the man who was from Cipher Pol No. 5
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.42,0:03:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and arrested Tom's Workers red-handed for\Nattacking the Judicial Ship eight years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! Spanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"M"! You're missing the "M"! It's "Spandam"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be very much looking forward\Nto your arrival at Enies Lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, guys! Hurry up and bring\Nthat criminal here already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! It's hot! It's hot! It's hot! Stupid lamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.91,0:03:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Roger.\N--Click.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Let me go, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:03:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold it, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.65,0:04:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You only shine for a second?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.32,0:04:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember right, you are...\None of the Straw Hats, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:07.08,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"The Truth Behind Her Betrayal!\NRobin's Sorrowful Decision!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.13,0:05:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only departure left today is\Nfor government personnel, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.72,0:05:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think they have to travel when Aqua\NLaguna is about to hit. Must be a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know that some real big shots\Nare gonna get on today's special train?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.56,0:05:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you taking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what I overheard when the\NNavy people were talking earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but these big shots seem to have been\Non a secret mission in Water Seven
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.61,0:05:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the past several years,\Nhiding their true identities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Secret mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.49,0:05:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I don't know what they\Nwere actually doing, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.33,0:05:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiding their true identities?\NThen it might be people we know, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.38,0:05:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, I kinda\Nthink I know who they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.97,0:06:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Who are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.06,0:06:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Do you think I'm wrong?\N--What?! From the backstreets?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sometimes see those guys\Nhaving secret conversations
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.32,0:06:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the corner at Blueno's bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.57,0:06:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not enough reason\Nto suspect them, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.03,0:06:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But despite the fact that they don't\Nwork much, they're quite prosperous, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.62,0:06:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They often take the first-class cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.92,0:06:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? In any case, we'll know who they\Nare when they get on the sea train later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.09,0:06:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet this will be the talk of\Nthe whole town tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.51,0:06:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't working! The wind is too strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.02,0:06:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fire isn't going out at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.44,0:07:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If people are still inside,\Nthey'll be done for if this keeps up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg-san...! Paulie-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami... Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to... treat her... right... away...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Give them treatment!\NThey've got terrible burns!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.70,0:07:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What're we gonna do with this reindeer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.04,0:07:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Him, too! He saved their lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're right. Hey! Give me a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:08:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got his butt whipped...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.89,0:08:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, in short, you're no longer\Npart of the Straw Hats,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.85,0:08:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you still haven't quit being a pirate, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.78,0:08:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a pirate, then we'll take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.15,0:08:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Kalifa!\N--Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.32,0:08:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't take it down yet, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't you dare touch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.38,0:08:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?! Hey! Are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.47,0:08:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although it was an assumed identity,\Nwe are recognized shipwrights in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:09:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should listen when we say\Nit's no good no matter what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?! Just leave her alone!\NShe's not even your ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.99,0:09:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will release the water, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Don't do anything stupid! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.59,0:09:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.32,0:09:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll carry you guys for a little bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.38,0:10:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.23,0:10:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move back! It's gonna collapse!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.15,0:10:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.07,0:10:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Isn't there anything we can do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg-san has recovered consciousness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.89,0:10:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief! He's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.26,0:10:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to that reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.97,0:11:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I heard that he's a pet of the Straw Hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.69,0:11:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! This one, too! The woman woke up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What're we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we make her tell us the\NStraw Hats' whereabouts now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's severely injured.\NAnd she's a woman, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg-san! You shouldn't move around yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.55,0:11:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys... give us some space.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.39,0:11:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna talk to this woman alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what he wants to\Ntalk alone with her about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.59,0:12:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! What'd you do that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit standing around! Lucci-san and\Nthe others may still be inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.18,0:12:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us a hand, you idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.97,0:12:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.18,0:12:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.27,0:12:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.19,0:12:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.69,0:12:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We falsely accused you of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.86,0:12:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll clear up the misunderstanding later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna talk about Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did that woman change after\Nyou guys came to this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.63,0:12:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After she went out to town,\Nshe suddenly disappeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.67,0:12:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and by this morning, she was the\Nsuspect of your attempted assassination.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.09,0:12:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When my friends finally found her,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.43,0:13:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she said she would no longer come back to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't know what was going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we came here tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.15,0:13:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to ask her directly again\Nwhy she's leaving the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.49,0:13:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To make my wish come true...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A wish that can never come true if I'm with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.16,0:13:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this wish that can never\Ncome true if she's with us...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you what I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.42,0:13:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably when you lost\Nsight of Nico Robin the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CP9...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.22,0:13:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Government's operation\Nwas already in progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is, of course, a reason\Nfor that woman's actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.02,0:13:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But before I tell you about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to know that Nico\NRobin and I both have a means
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.61,0:13:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to bring back the ancient weapon\Nthat could destroy the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.87,0:14:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.58,0:14:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.50,0:14:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A problem occurred in our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, come to the bedroom right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shoot Iceberg yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.72,0:14:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you get it, Nico Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The blueprints you guys were after are fakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.93,0:14:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I am to be killed, I won't give\Nthose blueprints to the Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're sniffing around\Nthe Poneglyphs on another front
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and helping the Government as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then I have to stop you right here, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.95,0:14:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not seeking the Poneglyphs\Nin order to bring the weapon back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.33,0:14:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to know the history, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a claim doesn't mean anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over... and over again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.01,0:15:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you don't intend to do so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.43,0:15:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weapons hurt people despite your intentions!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can even hurt those\Nwho mean a lot to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That which hurts people doesn't\Nnecessarily have malicious intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that simple curiosity of\Nwanting to know the history
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.57,0:15:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,leads to the destruction of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you should die right here,\Nright now, Nico Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.49,0:15:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after you saw the Ohara devils' fate,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.79,0:15:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you still want to chase\Nafter the world's history?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.50,0:15:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk like you know\Neverything about Ohara!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even know how much the\NWorld Government messed up my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.01,0:15:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hate the Government that much,\Nthen why are you helping them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.82,0:16:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I have a wish I want to come true\Neven if I have to give up everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're two conditions that\NCP9 forced on me in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One is to pin the assassination\Non the Straw Hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.17,0:16:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other is to turn myself in\Nto the Government and obey them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.80,0:16:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, you'll die, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you accept such conditions\Nafter evading them for 20 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.89,0:16:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this lone instance,\NCP9 has been given permission
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to exercise Buster Call against the Straw Hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.53,0:16:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buster Call?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.36,0:16:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an emergency order to\Nsummon five of the vice admirals
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from Navy Headquarters and\Nten battleships to one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.41,0:16:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you've been targeted by the\Nnational war-class military power,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nothing will remain of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, in the Navy, this authority\Nonly belongs to the three admirals
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.13,0:17:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the head of the Navy, the fleet admiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,through the admiral Aokiji,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.39,0:17:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CP9 was given the authority\Nto exercise it just this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.56,0:17:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't accept the conditions,\NBuster Call was going to be exercised on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.77,0:17:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I heard the name Aokiji, I gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was always able to make good\Nmy escape for the past 20 years
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because I had nothing to protect...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.16,0:17:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I could betray people\Nand use them as a shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I really can't do that any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The life I once gave up on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The heart that I lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dream I could no longer have...\NThey picked them all up for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.01,0:17:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to make friends who\Nwould believe in someone like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.98,0:18:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, your wish is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.48,0:18:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That the six Straw Hats, excluding me,\Ncan leave this island safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.53,0:18:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying, for that, you don't care\Nif the weapon is brought back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't care what happens to the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.12,0:18:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of that nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.43,0:18:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all people,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.41,0:18:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,over the lives of everyone in this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.95,0:18:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she chose the lives of the six of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.62,0:19:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I might have the weapon's\Nblueprints taken away by them,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.30,0:19:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the right to criticize her, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.64,0:19:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.73,0:19:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Robin didn't betray us after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.28,0:19:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better gather everyone\Nimmediately and let them know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.82,0:19:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Iceberg-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.91,0:19:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Straw Hat and the others were beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.99,0:19:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you can do now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.16,0:19:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Now"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It starts now! Luffy and the others are fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.34,0:19:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd take a lot more than that to take them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna get Robin back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.34,0:19:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When unsure, anyone can be weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.47,0:19:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no limit to their strength\Nwhen they know it's okay to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.14,0:20:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper! Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.81,0:20:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper! Wake up! We have to find everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.07,0:20:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper! Hey, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.40,0:20:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, he's really\Nseriously injured, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up! Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go join Luffy and the others and tell\Nthem everything that just happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...without leaving a single word out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.08,0:20:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.96,0:20:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll part ways here for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.46,0:20:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't worry. I won't do anything reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.43,0:20:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.93,0:20:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder... if Robin doesn't like us anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.65,0:20:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.48,0:20:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.28,0:20:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.24,0:20:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a woman lies...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.41,0:20:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a real man forgives her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.04,0:21:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For today's last service to\NEnies Lobby, departing at 11 PM,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.71,0:21:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please board from the second floor\Nlobby due to the raised water level.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.05,0:21:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Okay, let's go check them out!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.56,0:21:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since this involves a secret operation,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.39,0:21:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're forbidden to see them board.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.81,0:21:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, darn...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.99,0:21:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were chased after for the past 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.16,0:21:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised that you gave up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.67,0:21:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.70,0:22:19.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We had a dream that day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.20,0:22:24.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Our belief in ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.04,0:22:32.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,makes us able to cross the wildly surging ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.22,0:22:41.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You're braver and more caring than anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.81,0:22:50.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever depart this ship\Nand live in a different world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.94,0:23:00.94,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, we can all surely smile
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.13,0:23:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, it's not that Robin\Ndoesn't like us anymore?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.30,0:23:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! We'll all go and rescue her!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.68,0:23:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go! Where are Luffy and Zoro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.09,0:23:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to hurry up and find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.55,0:23:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only thirty minutes left\Nbefore the sea train departs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.68,0:23:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.18,0:23:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll fight for you no matter\Nwho we're up against!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.48,0:23:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.85,0:23:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Steam Whistle Forces Friends Apart!\NThe Sea Train Starts to Run"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.11,0:23:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
